We can use diffrent tools to crack the passwords 

Option 1) CrackMapExec :- We can use Crackmapexec to crack the password for diffrent protocols like SMB, FTP, mssql, ssh etc. 
              #crackmapexec <proto> <target-IP> -u <user or userlist> -p <password or passwordlist>
                e.g. crackmapexec winrm 10.129.42.197 -u user.list -p password.list
                e.g. crackmapexec winrm 10.129.42.197 -U username -p password.list :- When we have the username 
                e.g  crackmapexec winrm 10.129.42.197 -u user.list -P <Password> :- When we have password and checking if one else is using the same password. 
